zh-cn: 九三学社黑龙江省委员会

description.zh-cn: 九三学社在黑龙江省的地方组织，行政级别为正厅级。
description.en: The local organization of the Jiusan Society in Heilongjiang Province, with a departmental-level administrative ranking.

description.zh-cn: 九三学社的中央领导机构。
description.en: The central leading body of the Jiusan Society.

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国的民主党派之一。
description.en: One of the democratic parties of the People's Republic of China.

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国东北部的一个省级行政区。
description.en: A provincial-level administrative region in Northeast China.

description.zh-cn: 中华人民共和国政治术语，指在中国大陆范围内，除中国共产党以外的八个参政党的统称。
description.en: A political term in the People's Republic of China, referring to the eight legally-recognized political parties other than the Communist Party of China that participate in the government.

relationships.source: 九三学社黑龙江省委员会

description.zh-cn: 根据信息框，九三学社黑龙江省委员会的上级机构是九三学社中央委员会。
description.en: According to the infobox, the superior organization of the Jiusan Society Heilongjiang Provincial Committee is the Jiusan Society Central Committee.

relationships.source: 九三学社黑龙江省委员会

description.zh-cn: 九三学社黑龙江省委员会是九三学社在黑龙江省的地方组织。
description.en: The Jiusan Society Heilongjiang Provincial Committee is the local organization of the Jiusan Society in Heilongjiang Province.

relationships.source: 九三学社黑龙江省委员会

description.zh-cn: 九三学社黑龙江省委员会作为九三学社的地方组织，属于中国的民主党派。
description.en: As a local organization of the Jiusan Society, the Jiusan Society Heilongjiang Provincial Committee belongs to China's democratic parties.

relationships.source: 九三学社黑龙江省委员会

description.zh-cn: 九三学社黑龙江省委员会是九三学社在黑龙江省设立的地方组织，其活动范围主要在黑龙江省。
description.en: The Jiusan Society Heilongjiang Provincial Committee is the local organization of the Jiusan Society established in Heilongjiang Province, and its activities are primarily within Heilongjiang Province.
